[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=karaf.git;h=c5143c8&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=karaf.git;h=c5143c8&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-4475&quot; title=&quot;Performing status check will wipe cache if karaf.clean.all/karaf.clean.cache is set&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KARAF-4475&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KARAF-4475&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Do not wipe karaf cache and data dir while karaf is running.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ConfigurationProperties was used as &quot;Parser&quot; for karaf config, by status and stop scripts.&lt;br/&gt;
This change moves all &quot;state modifications&quot; to a separate method which is only called by Main&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
